# Changelog <!-- Newer dates on top -->

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-20
### Fixed
- Adjust `Consumer Track Packages` UI.
- Adjust `Order History` margins.
- Adjust popups designs and layout.
- Adjust `Driver` UI styles and layout.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-20
### Fixed
- Standardized order modal styling across driver and business interfaces.
- Implemented proper status-based icon coloring in order modals.
- Fixed modal overlay and content cutoff issues.
- Improved modal positioning and background handling.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-19
### Added
- Implemented multiple address management in Consumer PWA.
- Added ability to set and change default delivery address.

### Fixed
- Changes the user location marker on maps to a red pin for better visibility
- Updates the map container styling to match business interface design
- Fix the lightening address not changing issue in business
- Fix description section in business profile

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-18
### Fixed
- Fix `Business Add Product` modal spacing, margins and paddings for a better UI consistency.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-18
### Fixed
- Adjust `Checkout` UI margins, paddings and layouts for a better UI consistency.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-18
### Added
- Added confirmation dialog for product deletion to prevent accidental removals.
- Implemented user-friendly warning message for irreversible actions.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-17
### Fixed
- Fixed all `fuente apps` border width to align with the new design guidelines.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-14
### Fixed
- Adjust `courier list` and `courier pubkey form` for a better user experience
- Implemented styles for the "Unauthorized" screen based on the provided design.
- Fixed `exchange screen` spacing and alignment for a better readability
- Update `admin business` UI colors for improved visual consistency.
- Enhanced banner display in business profile with proper image containment and responsive behavior.

### Added
- Added automatic UI updates for product list when adding or modifying products.
- Implemented automatic modal closure after successful product addition.
- Added toast notifications for product operations feedback.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-13
### Fixed
- Fixed `driver registration flow` by displaying `public key` and approval status message instead of infinite loading screen when awaiting admin verification.
- Fixed navigation issue on key recovery page caused by missing `ToastProvider`.
- Fixed `admin general styles`: line breaks, title fonts, margins, and paddings to align with branding guidelines.
- Fixed `driver registration flow` by displaying `public key` and approval status message instead of infinite loading screen when awaiting admin verification.
- Fixed navigation issue on key recovery page caused by missing `ToastProvider`.
- Fixed `admin general styles`: line breaks, title fonts, margins, and paddings to align with branding guidelines.
- Fixed `driver registration flow` by displaying `public key` and approval status message instead of infinite loading screen when awaiting admin verification.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-02-12
### Added
- Added `CHANGELOG.md` doc to properly track dev process.
- Added `toast notification` in category section when a new category is added.

### Fixed
- Fixed `consumer_pwa` general styling.
